{{> header title="Your nbn® service’s Maximum Attainable Upload Speed"}}

<tr>
  <td style="padding: 20px 15px;">
    <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%">
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; color: {{brand.colors.headerText}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          <strong>Your nbn® service’s Maximum Attainable Upload Speed</strong>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          Hi %%NAME%%,
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          We are writing to inform you that we have checked your nbn® connection and found that you cannot receive the maximum upload internet speeds for your plan. As a result, in the next few days we will provide you with a refund. We will also give you a choice of three options below.
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          <strong>You are currently paying for our %%PLAN%% plan which has maximum speeds of %%DOWNLOAD_MAX_SPEED%% Mbps download and %%UPLOAD_MAX_SPEED%% Mbps upload.</strong>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          The maximum speeds you can actually receive are %%DOWNLOAD_ACTUAL_SPEED%% Mbps download and %%UPLOAD_ACTUAL_SPEED%% Mbps upload.
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          As you cannot receive the maximum upload speeds for your plan, we will refund you $%%REFUND_AMOUNT%%. The refund will be credited to your {{brand.displayName}} account unless you tell us otherwise. If you were on a different nbn® speed plan prior to your current plan and also could not receive the maximum internet speeds for that plan, your refund will take into account your current and previous nbn® plans with {{brand.displayName}}.
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; color: {{brand.colors.headerText}}; padding-bottom: 8px;">
          <strong>Your options</strong>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          As you cannot receive the maximum upload speeds for your plan, you can choose between the following options.
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; color: {{brand.colors.headerText}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          <strong>Option 1 - Remain on your current nbn® plan and receive a refund</strong>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          You can choose to remain on your current nbn® plan and receive the refund as advised above. You should know that you will not receive the full benefit of your current nbn® plan because your nbn® connection still cannot provide the maximum upload plan speed.
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          If you want to choose this option, you don’t need to do anything. The refund will be credited to your {{brand.displayName}} account unless you tell us otherwise.
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; color: {{brand.colors.headerText}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          <strong>Option 2 – Move plans and receive a refund</strong>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          You can choose to move to a lower speed plan that your line can support. If you choose this option, you will not be charged a change of plan fee and you will receive a refund as advised above.
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          To select this option, please call us on {{brand.support.phone}}.
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; color: {{brand.colors.headerText}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          <strong>Option 3 – Exit your service without cost and receive a refund</strong>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          You may wish to terminate your service with {{brand.displayName}}. If you choose this option, you will not be charged a termination fee and {{brand.displayName}} will issue you a refund.
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          To select this option, please call us on {{brand.support.phone}}.
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; color: {{brand.colors.headerText}}; padding-bottom: 8px;">
          <strong>Important things to note</strong>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          Your maximum speed is a limit on what speeds you can receive, not a measurement of what you are actually receiving at all times. Actual speeds will vary based on several factors such as modem capabilities and internet traffic demand.  If you’re interested, <a href="%%READ_MORE%%" style="color: {{brand.colors.primary}}; text-decoration: underline;">read more</a> about what affects speed.
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          Your maximum speed may not change if you choose to exit your service with {{brand.displayName}} and purchase an nbn® internet plan from another provider. If you choose to exit your service with {{brand.displayName}} and purchase an nbn® internet plan from another provider, we recommend you ask your new provider what speeds they can provide, and what speeds you will receive during busy times.
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; color: {{brand.colors.headerText}}; padding-bottom: 8px;">
          <strong>What you need to do next</strong>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          You need to select one of the options:
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          <ul style="padding-left: 20px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">
            <li style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 8px;">If you would like to stay on your current plan and receive a refund, you don't need to do anything; or</li>
            <li style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 8px;">If you would like move plans or exit your service without cost, please call us on {{brand.support.phone}}.</li>
          </ul>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          If you have any questions, we can help. Just call us on {{brand.support.phone}}.
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </td>
</tr>

<tr>
  <td style="padding: 20px 15px 60px;">
    <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%">
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}};">
          Thanks,<br>
          Your {{brand.displayName}} Team
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </td>
</tr>

{{> footer showThingsHeading=true showNbnTrademark=true typicalEveningSpeed=true}}
